 wordt deze zomer De slimste mens? Onder leiding van Philip Freriks en het kritisch oog van jurylid Maarten van Rossem gaan dagelijks drie prominente Nederlanders de strijd aan in de vragenarena.","category":"Spelshow, Documentaire"},"90":{"channel":"boW4lYH6CESbHzgZais_lQAAAAI","start":"1626451210","end":"1626452739","first":"N","idtitle":"NOSJOURNAAL","title":"NOS Journaal","program_id":"A9ECBB76B3C6203C4F17431A0D81E968","date":"","icon":"https:\/\/images.nlziet.nl\/metadataimportimages\/source\/57B99DA8E4E88FC33CBA86CAC90CCECC2D2A3AA06EF0E18ADE60142D0F1E6F2C.jpg","description":"Met het laatste nieuws, gebeurtenissen van nationaal en internationaal belang en het weer.","category":"Nieuws"},"91":{"channel":"boW4lYH6CESbHzgZais_lQAAAAI","start":"1626452739","end":"1626453211","first":"N","idtitle":"NOSJOURNAALREGIO","title":"NOS Journaal Regio","program_id":"73674BBD3A2F9787D35337947F332266","date":"","icon":"https:\/\/images.nlziet.nl\/metadataimportimages\/source\/366D2786F040CD01AD379D013EB8387F0B591E39463063C2C2C971487A10BC82.jpg","description":"","category":""},"92":{"channel":"boW4lYH6CESbHzgZais_lQAAAAI","start":"1626453211","end":"1626454676","first":"N","idtitle":"NOORDZUIDOOSTWEST","title":"Noord-Zuid-Oost-West","program_id":"E19D4198A0DB2BA9C2628FC954B3CE63","date":"","icon":"https:\/\/images.nlziet.nl\/metadataimportimages\/source\/64E959ACE0879A5031D12382E93AF8DB76E684B33907744055F6F784FE9C7DC1.jpg","description":"","category":""},"93":{"channel":"boW4lYH6CESbHzgZais_lQAAAAI","start":"1626454676","end":"1626456497","first":"B","idtitle":"BINNENSTEBUITEN","title":"BinnensteBuiten","program_id":"A652F7CE645C0F39B2331E757E1CAABC","date":"","icon":"https:\/\/images.nlziet.nl\/metadataimportimages\/source\/E74C3BAE6D877382E796C7509C1E6A9FAAA5E9BED5AEE0EDDC8D08C7CEC59F11.jpg","description":"","category":""},"94":{"channel":"boW4lYH6CESbHzgZais_lQAAAAI","start":"1626456497","end":"1626458228","first":"D","idtitle":"DESTREKENVANVANBOVEN","title":"De streken van